@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1 class="page-title fw-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>

<p>
    OrchidApp does not collect, analyse, sell or share personal data for
    analytics, marketing or profiling purposes.
</p>

<p>
    The application does not use tracking cookies, third-party services,
    embedded external scripts or hidden telemetry.
</p>

<p>
    OrchidApp stores only the information intentionally entered by the user
    for the purpose of managing an orchid collection. All data remains within
    the hosting environment controlled by the system operator.
</p>

<p>
    Database backups are encrypted prior to leaving the host device. No
    unencrypted database data is transmitted to external systems.
</p>

<p>
    OrchidApp is a self-hosted application. The operator of the hosting
    environment is responsible for infrastructure, security and access
    control.
</p>
